body:
I was restricted from playing another game for 30 mins, though it wasn&#039;t my fault because the client kept reconnecting and disconnecting. I think it&#039;s unfair that you get punished for something you can&#039;t control. It&#039;s not that my internet is bad either because I usually have 4-3 bars.
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 

I think Riot needs to change this because players can&#039;t predict when they&#039;re going to disconnect, though it might be hard for the system to recognize a disconnection, I don&#039;t think that it&#039;s fair to punish players because they disconnected during the selection screen.
